nodes.text: Keizar-Volvec was the manufacturer of a variety of vehicles, including Podracers, airspeeders, and starships. Among its most well-known products were sublight engines for star cruisers. Based on the Outer Rim world Temako, Keizar-Volvec products were trusted by buyers for being well made and sturdy, if not unexciting and bland. Its first Podracer design, the 9T9-B Wasp, maintained the company's reputation for unimaginative engineering.
